# Drift Demo - AI Prompts (Token-Optimized)

## CHEAT SHEET - Preferred tools (low token usage)

drift status              # Small response, good overview
drift pack list           # Shows available packs
drift pack name="api"     # Cached, compact context
drift export format="summary" compact=true
drift where "pattern"     # Targeted, small responses
drift files <path>        # Single file focus
drift dna format="summary"
drift mutations           # Usually small
drift boundaries action="overview"

## AVOID in demos (high token usage)

drift patterns categories=["x","y","z"]  # Returns ALL patterns with full metadata
drift examples                            # Returns actual code snippets
drift export format="ai-context"          # Full verbose output

---

## SECTION 1: Python / FastAPI
cd drift/test-repos/competitive-intelligence-api

Give me a quick status overview of patterns in this codebase

What auth patterns exist? (use drift where "auth")

Show me patterns in the middleware folder (use drift files)

